    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional example of the E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 powerplant with its signature 8,400 RPM redline. This unit retains its factory-honed mechanical integrity, with the rod bearings and throttle actuators preemptively addressed to ensure peak operational longevity. The six-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, short-throw engagement, channeling torque through a perfectly calibrated M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis remains taut, utilizing Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for precise lateral dynamics without any bushing deflection. Finished in Interlagos Blue over Novillo leather, the bodywork exhibits flawless original paint depth and a pristine, UV-protected carbon fiber roof panel. This is a turn-key, collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
